OL,3,CPeston: Will Burnham regret ousting
OL,4,CStarmer?
OL,6,FAndy Burnham will be Britain's next
OL,7,Fprime minister, probably in less than
OL,8,Fa month, barring a gaffe or scandal of
OL,9,Fsuch enormity that we'd all need years
OL,10,Fof therapy.
OL,12,FThe last remaining Starmerites huff
OL,13,Fand puff at the injustice of the
OL,14,Feviction of their hero. They warn that
OL,15,Funless Burnham is tested in a
OL,16,Fleadership election, he could turn out
OL,17,Fto be the booby prize in a lucky dip.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
