OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782211684
OL,3,CPeston: Will Burnham regret ousting
OL,4,CStarmer?
OL,6,FLabour's more left-wing MPs - the
OL,7,FCampaign group - will do their normal
OL,8,Fthing of agonising about which of them
OL,9,Fshould be the candidate of the true
OL,10,Ffaith, though there is zero chance
OL,11,Fthat any one of them could get the
OL,12,Frequisite 81 nominations.
OL,14,FThe only semi-credible challenger
OL,15,Fwould have been the former health
OL,16,Fsecretary Wes Streeting, but he has
OL,17,Ftoday announced that he and Burnham
OL,18,Fagree on everything that matters -
OL,19,Fwhich presumably means on the
OL,20,Fcompelling idea that Streeting should
OL,21,Fhave a big Cabinet job.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
