OL,3,CPeston: Will Burnham regret ousting
OL,4,CStarmer?
OL,6,F"Wes would make a very good
OL,7,Fchancellor," one minister said to me
OL,8,Fwryly.
OL,10,FSo, Burnham will be the seventh UK PM
OL,11,Fsince David Cameron stepped down just
OL,12,Funder a decade ago, and probably as
OL,13,Fsoon as Friday, 17 July.
OL,15,FHang out the union flag bunting?
OL,17,FWell, not if you think economies
OL,18,Fprosper on a foundation of political
OL,19,Fstability.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@LO]
