OL,3,CPeston: Will Burnham regret ousting
OL,4,CStarmer?
OL,6,FAnd not until we can assess whether
OL,7,FBurnham can revive the economy and
OL,8,Fliving standards in the tax and
OL,9,Fborrowing straitjacket imposed by
OL,10,FLabour's 2024 election manifesto, when
OL,11,Fthat same manifesto imposes huge
OL,12,Frestrictions on improving commercial
OL,13,Faccess to the European Union's massive
OL,14,Fsingle market, and when the
OL,15,Frecalcitrance of Labour MPs are a
OL,16,Fbrake on his ability to streamline
OL,17,Fboth welfare state and Whitehall.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
